data.value: Digital HealthCare is developed with the intention to make life easier while dealing with medical care field. All the included features in the software will greatly improve the experience of all users including patient, doctor, hospital. Main features included in the software are for patients: finding hospitals and doctors, easy online booking, pay hospitals and doctors, recieve prescriptions and medical reports; for hospitals and doctors: manage bookings, set unavailable days for booking, manage hospital tests, set booking fee, manage payments and check incomes etc. Overall its a hassle free easy to use healthcare management system aiming to prevent loosing any important medical documents and keep all the tracks of medical history accurately.
